entries.femaleVariant: One second, boss... Brad? Hey, Brad!
Listen, boss, you help me out? Kids on the block been up my ass lately, and you seem real tough...
[Stand] Sure, I'll help.
Might as well, since I'm here. Lead the way.
Not my bike, not my biz. Simple as that.
[Stand] You're on your own.
Thanks, boss. All right, follow me.
Oh well, can't force you. Just have to do it myself.
You lost your minds? Get you grubby paws off my bike?
You think we're playing around? This a small price to pay for fuckin' treason!
Fuck you want? This ain't none o' your biz!
Leave him alone.
You fuckin' deaf?
Never mind. I'll just be on my way.
You forget how to speak, huh?
You hear me? Speak up or fuck off.
You're gettin' back at corps by stealin' from a street vendor? Oh, that says a lot about you. Now back the fuck away from him.
entries.maleVariant: You're gettin' back at corps by stealin' from a street vendor? Says a lot about you. Now back the fuck away from him.

entries.femaleVariant: Know what? You're right, this ain't my biz. Do whatever you want.
Or you'll do what?
You think I need your fuckin' permission?!
Please, boss! Don't leave me like this!
You still can't let go of that? Shenna made a choice – you should be proud of her!
I'll blow your brains out.
I could break your jaw, fracture your skull, shoot you... the possibilities are endless.
I changed my mind. Do whatever you want.
You know what? You're right, this ain't my biz. Do whatever you want.
You care so much about a rat-fuckin' traitor – then you can die together!
Smart move, shitbag. Now get lost before you catch any stray lead.
Eh, don't worry about it. I've had worse. No-good fucking deadbeats!
Anyway... stop by whenever you around. I throw in a nice discount for you!
Sure thing, boss. Thanks.
Give it up, Darrell, nobody gives a shit about you. Let this be a warning.
Come on, let's go before 6th Street shows up.
[Punch]
You OK?
Now that that's over, you OK?
What's going on here?
Relax, don't got any beef with you... for now. What happened?
Your new pal here talked his sister into taking a job at Zetatech. Bitch just leaves and doesn't even say bye?!
Yo, Brad. Ain't that... yo, that's the bitch everyone been talkin' about. One that came back from the dead!
entries.maleVariant: Yo, Brad. Ain't that... yo, that's the dude everyone been talkin' about. One that came back from the dead!

entries.femaleVariant: Now that that's over, you OK?
Who, me? Couldn't be better! All talk and no action, hehe. Maybe they should go get a job! Fucking parasites...
Anyway... stop by whenever you around. I throw in a nice discount for you.
Will do, boss. Thanks.
You OK?
Have they lost their damn minds?! Thanks, boss. That oughta teach 'em.
Fuck! Knocked him flat!
See you around! And tell your sister I said "Hi!"
Proud?! That bitch sold out to a fucking corp! Now it's time for payback!
You another corpo-rat?
What about your sister's new job?
We been runnin' these streets ever since we were kids! Hacking streetvending machines, fuckin' up corpos... S'what we live for!
And what? Now she's too good for us?! Double-crossing cunt!
You listen to yourselves? And how's stealin' from poor folk like me gonna make things better?
You know how many gonks she offed already? And I ain't even talkin' s-solo...
entries.maleVariant: You know how many gonks he's offed already? And I ain't even talkin' s-solo...

entries.femaleVariant: Shit... she followin' us?
You really so mad Shenna got corp-job instead of doing whatever it is you do all day?
Know what? I changed my mind. Fuck this corpo-lover up!
And tell your sister to fuck off to another neighborhood, or next time we're coming for her brother!
At least her life is going somewhere! So stay the fuck out of it and move on!
Shenna's a grown-ass woman now. You should follow her example!
Well, at least Shenna can focus on her job now. No one in the family ever got as high up as her.
Well, at least Shenna can focus on her job now. No one in the family ever got as high up as her.
Vance? Vance, wh-what you think you're doing?!
'Course, if I ever see her again! New job's been tough on her lately.
Just between the two of us... you really proud your sister's joined the Zetatech fold?
What about your sister's new job?
Look, I know what you thinking. "Corps are exploiting us," "They're turning us into slaves." That's what people say, no?
Well, guess what? They never have to worry 'bout puttin' food on table. Me and Shenna take whatever we can get.
She's probably runnin' on neurostims. You're not worried?
Hey, you can't have it all. And even if we did, nobody get off their ass and do anything!
Well, when you put it that way...
Up till now we almost got used to them... but to pull a knife on one of their own?
[Sit] Can I get a Chromanticore?
Need a little pick-me-up. You got Chromanticore?
Some water. You got Sain Ruisseau?
[Sit] Sain Ruisseau, please.
[Sit] I'll have a Lothbrok.
I get a beer here? Lothbrok, maybe?
The hell you want that swill for, boss? Heard some batches even glow in the dark!
Why drink poison when you can drink Spunkey Monkey? Way better than--
Ooof, boss – water? You don't want something with taste?
Water is for the animals! People didn't invent sugar just to drink--
Sorry, boss. No beer here.
Whaddaya got?
Maybe something apricot-flavor? Some people say this gives them hiccups, but they lie! I never had--
You freeze up a lot?
